description: Welcome to 2 Bishop Road! This immaculate, beautiful, lovingly cared for 2 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom townhouse, with an extra bonus room ideal as an office/guest room, is right in the Heart of West Hartford! Walking distance to the popular Blue Back square and West Hartford Center, with it's many shops, entertainment & fantastic restaurants. Step inside the open and airy kitchen which features a breakfast bar, marble counters, recessed lighting, an island, stainless steel appliances, built ins, and lovely white sub tile backsplash. Gracious floor plan (with rich hardwood flooring) unfolds light filled stylish spacious rooms, ideal for gathering with family and friends. Get cozy in the electric fireplaced living room with a beautiful white wood background. The bedrooms feature warm neutral tones and walk in closets. This property has an office featuring a barn door as well as many other unique updates. Washer/dryer conveniently located inside the unit. Elevator leads to the third floor making for a private location. Cool rooftop patio and private workout facilities are just a few of the many attributes this home has to offer. This is one of West Hartford's newest Condo developments and this one is unique as well as an end unit and on the top floor. All 3 bathrooms are remodeled. Modern, warm and welcoming. Plenty of storage space as well! A must see. Book your showing today, it may be gone tomorrow.

description: This large freestanding unit at The Reservoir is truly special. The original owners are selling their meticulously cared for Willow Elite, which has been upgraded to the highest standards and sits on a private spot at the end of a cul-de-sac.This home is open and bright, with 9+ ceilings and large windows; the light from French Doors in the Great Room shines through as soon as you enter. Adjacent to the Foyer, the Dining Room has been made even grander with an enlarged niche wall and cathedral ceilings. The Great Room has a beautiful gas fireplace and room enough for both ample seating and a grand piano.French Doors lead out to a large deck that overlooks your beautiful, wooded lot. The kitchen is well appointed with stainless Bosch appliances, solid cherry cabinetry & a wonderful Morning Room with lots of windows for table seating. There’s a pantry closet, laundry & powder room as well as convenient access to the 3-car garage. On the other side of the Foyer, the Living Area is comprised of a cozy, gas fireplaced den, a large bedroom and full bath, and a Primary Suite boasting a great big walk-in closet, and a bathroom that’s light and bright with a wall of windows, double sinks, and a walk-in glass shower. In the Lower Level, there’s another room for recreation and walk-out access to the garden, plus a 3rd bedroom for guests, another full bath, 2 large closets, and ample storage space in the large unfinished areas. This 3,245 home is equipped with a 22kw back-up generator and is conveniently located across the street from miles of hiking and biking trails, with easy access to West Hartford Center, Blue Back Square, Uconn Medical Center, and Corbin’s Corner Shops. Short drive to the highway and Farmington Village.  Fabulous location for easy living.

37 Emily Way, West Hartford, CT 06107 is a condo home that contains 2,528 sq ft and was built in 2004. It contains 2 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms. This home last sold for $710,000 in November 2022. 
 
The Zestimate for this house is $678,600. The Rent Zestimate for this home is $4,099/mo.

Delightful Preston Model, and rare end-unit, in desirable Quaker Green.  Ideal unit location steps from gazebo, pool, playground, clubhouse, rec. center, gym, all within the beautiful and landscaped community.  Inviting interior layout, which greets you with formal living, complimented by vaulted ceilings and adjacent dining room.  Convenient first floor primary bedroom with spacious closets and bath suite.  Recent upgrades include 2020 hot water heater, 2021 A/C compressor, exterior pavers patio, and newly painted lower level.  Total sq. ft. over 3,000 inclusive of everything!  Short distance from New Britain Ave shopping center, Beachland Park and i-84.  A must see in West Hartford!

71 Emily Way, West Hartford, CT 06107 is a condo home that contains 3,000 sq ft and was built in 2003. It contains 3 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms. This home last sold for $695,000 in October 2022. 
 
The Zestimate for this house is $705,600. The Rent Zestimate for this home is $4,169/mo.

Rarely available Elm Elite large freestanding ranch at The Reservoir with attached 3-car garage, finished lower level for guests to spread out, and lots of brand-new updates. The main living floor offers 9’+ ceilings, fresh paint and newly refinished hardwood floors throughout.  Off the columned Foyer, the Living and Dining Rooms, featuring cathedral ceilings, cove lighting, and impressive trim work, lead to a recently updated kitchen with stainless appliances, quartz countertops, and gleaming white cabinets.  There’s a wonderful circular Breakfast Nook with lots of morning light, and an attached Family Room with a gas burning fireplace and French door leading out to a private wood deck. The Primary bedroom suite is spacious and bright, with a bathroom that’s updated with all the amenities: double sinks, jetted tub, stone counters, frameless glass-walk in shower. There’s a separate Office with French Door, and a guest bedroom, a second full bath, powder room, and laundry room that leads to the 3-car garage.  The Lower Level has a 30x15 recreation room that offers a ton of possibilities, another bedroom with lots of closets, including a large walk-in that’s cedar lined, and a third full bathroom.  Full-sized windows and high ceilings everywhere provide a lot of nature light.  There’s plenty of unfinished space that’s ready to be made into more living space or keep as is for tons of storage. The Reservoir is easy living with extensive walking trails, pathways filled with... flowers, shrubs, a pond, and a gazebo on site. Located just across street from MDC enjoy more biking and walking trails. Conveniently down the road from West Hartford Center, Farmington Village, Uconn Medical Center, highways, and the Mall. A great place to call home.

96 Emily Way, West Hartford, CT 06107 is a condo home that contains 2,220 sq ft and was built in 2004. It contains 2 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. This home last sold for $560,000 in October 2022. 
 
The Zestimate for this house is $555,400. The Rent Zestimate for this home is $3,246/mo.

Rare opportunity to own a 4th floor larger unit in the much sought after Fernwood Estates 55+ complex! This unit has been refreshed with new carpeting in the two generous bedrooms and most surfaces have been freshly painted. This unit is amazing with coffered ceiling, granite and stainless kitchen, a separate laundry room and views, views and more views! When you enter this incredible complex you will feel like you've entered a fancy hotel/spa. The foyer is most welcoming and there is a tremendous community room that leads to an ample courtyard. There is a real community feel in this complex and owners meet for movie nights, BBQs, Monday happy hour, book clubs, holiday parties and more! Take the west elevator and here is where you will travel to the 4th floor, head south and enter this beautiful unit, 404! From the moment you enter this unit you will be taken with the sheer size and openness of the sun-drenched rooms. The living room has a gas fireplace, high ceilings and ample space for a dining area as well! A spacious kitchen area offers stainless appliances, handsome granite counters and a breakfast bar. You will not lack for cabinet space here! The primary bedroom is completely separate from the 2nd bedroom and has a generous walk-in closet and beautiful primary bath with double sink and granite. The second bedroom is also spacious, it too has a walk-in closet and granite bathroom with walk-in shower. This unit comes with 2 parking spaces and a double storage room.

Stunning and Immaculate freestanding condo in the highly sought-after Reservoir community!  The soaring ceilings, gleaming hardwood floors, abundant natural light and flowing spaces will make you fall in love the minute you enter.  The living room highlighted by a Vermont Castings gas fireplace offers a vaulted ceiling and opens to the bright eat-in kitchen with Corian counters, gas cooktop and a spacious pantry. Entertain in the formal dining room with floor-to-ceiling windows and cathedral ceiling. French doors open to a large study with a walk-in closet - the perfect quiet place to work or read.  The primary suite contains a roomy walk-in closet and spa bath with a relaxing jet-tub, separate shower and dual sinks.  The guest suite offers another full bath and walk-in closet.  A convenient main-level laundry room leads to the two-car garage. Other features include a private deck, welcoming covered front porch, pull-down attic access and a huge unfinished basement perfect for storage or future finishing! Updates include a newer Lennox furnace (2020) and new carpeting in the bedrooms.  The Reservoir is a lovely community with numerous walking trails and gardens and overlooks the famous West Hartford Reservoir!  Minutes to the downtown Center filled with restaurants and shops.  Possible for UNDER age 55, contact listing agent for details! Welcome Home!

Rarely Available, Spacious End Unit in Desirable Quaker Green!  Gorgeous custom Harrison model townhome with tons of upgrades.  Sun-filled open floor plan, gleaming hardwood floors throughout main level, wainscoting, granite and stainless white kitchen, freshly painted neutral color.  LR/DR opens to the maintenance free composite deck and back open space with meticulously manicured grounds- the perfect place to relax and unwind.  The large Primary Bedroom is on the 2nd floor and has a vaulted ceiling, sitting area, large ensuite bath with jetted tub, double vanity, walk-in shower, and huge walk-in closet.  Two more nicely sized bedrooms and a 2nd full bath complete this level.  The third floor Loft with its vaulted ceiling makes an excellent office space, playroom, study, or den.  The square footage does not include the daylight Lower Level which is fully finished with 3rd full bath, laundry area with new washer & dryer, and can serve as a 4th Bedroom, Media Room, Playroom, Guest Area or Family Room. Enjoy the carefree lifestyle at this very desirable and well-maintained complex complete with inground heated pool, playground, club house, billiards room and well-equipped fitness center.  Close to malls, Downtown WH shopping, restaurants and major highways it's the perfect place to call home in West Hartford.

Elegant condominium in The Heritage at Blue Back Square where shopping, dining and entertainment are just outside your door! Live in the center of West Hartford, a vibrant community with a wide assortment of excellent restaurants, boutique shops and a Whole Foods Market, all just a short walk from home. This well-designed fourth floor unit has open kitchen and living areas, flanked by the primary suite on one side, with gorgeous bath and walk-in closets, and a guest bedroom or study with a second full bath, on the other. The gourmet kitchen is finely appointed with a Wolf range, paneled Sub-Zero refrigerator and paneled dishwasher as well. Gleaming Brazilian Cherry floors, brand new, modern light fixtures and ceiling fans, freshly painted walls and trim, new window treatments...perfection! Through the tall windows or from your private balcony, you have coveted views of the town. There is front desk concierge service 7 days a week, two large common rooms for reading or socializing, and a kitchen that can be reserved for entertaining larger groups. Half-way between Boston and New York, whether a primary or second home, this is the place to be!

ONE OF A KIND UNIT AT THE RESERVOIR! Located at the beginning of 4 townhouses and the only ONE THAT HAS A SPECIAL SETTING AND VIEW AND LIVES LIKE A STAND ALONE UNIT. Look at the magnificent first floor space with its soaring ceilngs and open floor plan which incorporates a large living room space with a gas fireplace and a custom circular dining area. The large kitchen has a breakfast bar as well as a breakfast nook that could also be used as a sitting area. On the first floor is the master bedroom with 2  walk-in closets with an attached full bath with a walk-in shower.To complete the first floor is a half bath, the laundry and a door to the attached garage. Upstairs are 2 more bedrooms and another full bath plus a large loft area overlooking the first floor, perfect for a home office. The walkout basement is unfinished but could be another great living area. It is already plumbed for a bath. Off the living room is a deck which overlooks the woods. The view from the front windows of this unit is spectacular and it could all be yours! This unit needs some work but some lucky buyer can make it their own.

2 Harvest Ct, Newington, CT 06111 is a condo home that contains 1,974 sq ft and was built in 2014. It contains 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. This home last sold for $460,000 in September 2022. 
 
The Zestimate for this house is $469,900. The Rent Zestimate for this home is $2,985/mo.

18 Harvest Ct, Newington, CT 06111 is a condo home that contains 2,092 sq ft and was built in 2017. It contains 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. This home last sold for $465,000 in August 2022. 
 
The Zestimate for this house is $475,600. The Rent Zestimate for this home is $3,024/mo.

This unit is one of a kind-beautifully remodeled with the wall between kitchen and living area opened up.  It is a game changer. Recently updated kitchen and master bath.  In the kitchen the cabinets were refinished, new quartz countertops and backsplash added.  This is a gorgeous 3 bedroom, 2.1 bath Ives unit with a loft and wood floors throughout the first and second floors - an expensive upgrade! Immaculate wood floors, ceramic tiled bathrooms, an plenty of natural light, and a open floor plan to stay connected with family or friends. 3 generous sized bedrooms on the second floor including a master bedroom suite with walk- in closet, and large sunlit bathroom that has been updated with large tub and shower. The loft space offers a perfect getaway for game room, den, office, or workout room. The lower level is rough plumbed for a bath should you decide to install a dream basement down the road. Pretty patio off the living room for relaxing or entertaining or enjoy any one of the Quaker Green amenities including lounging at the heated inground pool, working out in the fitness center, playing a game of pool in the billiard's/game room or walking to one of the local restaurants, shops, or bars. This vibrant community is a fantastic place to call home and this an opportunity to get in for a great price. Oh one more fun detail...many home furnishings & TV's are included  (check out the inclusion/exclusion document for more details). Best & final offers by Monday 6/20 at 5pm.
Beautifully remodeled 2019. All the mechanicals, kitchen, bathrooms. Beautiful open concept contemporary space

Rare opportunity to purchase a remodeled ranch style unit, in a great location, in the beautiful Steeplechase condominium complex.  The open floor plan includes a gorgeous kitchen which is connected to the dining and living rooms.  The kitchen is well appointed with stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and a beautiful farm sink.  Cozy up to the gas fireplace in the living room or go through the french doors to the solarium.   The solarium connects to a private deck and yard with pretty park-like views inviting you to relax.  The primary suite has a large walk-in closet, a full bathroom and its own dedicated deck.  Who wouldn’t want an updated additional full bathroom on the first floor, a second bedroom and laundry?  The second floor has a beautiful loft space with a half bathroom.  There are architectural details throughout this home with soaring ceilings and hardwood floor.  This home has a full basement with ample storage and great options for a home gym or office, plus a two car attached garage.  The condo has been well maintained with a new furnace (2019), new central AC (2019), new 200-amp electric panel (2020), and newly finished hardwood floors so there’s nothing left to do but unpack!

Fantastic 3 bedroom Townhome style condo located in West Hartford. Welcome to Tumblebrook Estate. This well maintained and quiet complex is conveniently located in West Hartford just minutes to everything. You will be a short distance from Bishops Corner, public as well as private schools, golf courses, highways, shopping. places of worship and more. The first floors offers a large eat in kitchen, with an abundance of cabinet space and great southern light. The living room/dining room combination is also a large space and includes southern exposure, a gas fireplace and a French door to your private deck. A half bath rounds off the first floor. Be sure to notice the fantastic ceiling height on the first floor. On the second level you will find a laundry area and three bedrooms. Each bedroom is good size and the master suite includes a large walk in closet and large en-suite bath complete with double sinks, a tub and a separate shower. The fully finished lower level is a great bonus. With close to 800 feet it is the perfect space to hang out, watch TV, set up a game room or plenty of other options. The condo has gas heat, central air, a two car attached garage and is in move in condition. Come see it today!

A West Hartford Gem. Bright and SPACIOUS maintenance free living. Perfectly styled and visually stunning townhouse situated in the desirable Tumblebrook Estates community. This home is absolutely move in ready. Almost every inch has been thoughtfully renovated since purchased in 2017. The first level is ideal for entertaining and has bamboo flooring throughout. The fully updated kitchen features stainless steel appliances, large farmhouse sink, custom cabinetry, quartz countertops, and oversized island that leads into a southern light filled living room with 10ft ceilings and glass pane doors that open to a private deck. Dining room for special occasions with full wall built in pantry/coffee bar and powder room complete the first floor. An open foyer showcases the cable railing staircase. Upstairs, the primary suite offers space to relax, large custom walk-in closet and beautifully updated en suite bathroom with double sink, soaking tub, and tiled walk-in shower. Down the hall are two generous sized bedrooms, full bathroom and laundry room. The attached two car garage has built in cabinetry for ample storage. A spacious finished 800 square foot lower level is perfect for a fitness area, home office, or media room. 31 Harwich offers an unbeatable location. Quiet and private, yet just outside of Bishops corner, and close proximity to golf courses, parks, restaurants, shopping, public and private schools, as well as easy access to major commute routes. Showings begin Friday 5/20

Fabulous opportunity to rent this beautifully redone 3 bedroom unit at Tumblebrook estates on the corner of no.main street and Simsbury rd! gorgeous new kitchen, All new High Performance double Insulated Windows (keeps gas/electric bill low) and double insulated sliding glass door, new, High Capacity HVAC system, all new master bath, this is a unique unit with a full finished lower level with daylight windows and full bath. attached 2 car garage and spacious deck, backing to the woods. this popular complex designed by Tai Soo Kim has high ceilings and lots of light adding to the appeal in this very stylish and livable home!

Tenant pays for all utilities. Landlord pays for trash, snow removal and landscape

A must see!  Beautiful townhouse located near West Hartford Center.  No need for a car to visit all the nearby fabulous shops and dining establishments!  Inside you are greeted by 9 Foot ceilings, crown moldings, gorgeous tray ceilings, and gleaming hardwood floors.  The kitchen is outfitted with granite counters, stainless steel appliances and a breakfast bar - perfect for entertaining!  The living room will be your favorite spot - next to the fireplace nestled up with a good book in the evenings.  Upstairs there are two bedrooms and 2 full baths with stunning tile!   The master has a large walking closet!   Additional finished space in the lower level with a bathroom and additional room that can be used as an office or whatever your heart desires!  You have both a patio off the finished lower level and deck on the 2nd level - your choice of spaces to relax on those wonderful Connecticut summer nights!  Near highways, shopping, parks - it is truly the perfect location!

description: Located in the sought-after Quaker Green in West Hartford, just 2 miles from West Hartford Center and Blue Back Square. This rarely available 3-bedroom, 3.5 bathroom townhouse is freshly re-carpeted and ready for your personal touch. Enter through the attached one-car garage or front door to a spacious first floor living room, kitchen, and dining with gleaming hardwood floors. Half bath just off of the foyer. Outside, the privacy fence on both sides of the deck allows for more entertainment space and grilling at your back step. The second-floor features a large primary bedroom with high ceilings, walk in closet, en suite bathroom with walk in shower and jacuzzi tub, and double vanity. Second and third bedroom on this floor each have ample closet space and an additional full bathroom in the hallway. The laundry room is also conveniently located on this level. Continue up the finished open and airy third floor that can be used for a home office, gym, or both. A spacious fully finished basement has an additional full bathroom and could be utilized as a guest room or 4th bedroom. Enjoy the outstanding community amenities including pool, gym, and clubhouse center. Walk just steps outside of Quaker Green to Beachland park or into Elmwood to enjoy the local shops and restaurants. Rare opportunity not to be missed, take the time to explore all that 47 Park Place has to offer!

90 Emily Way, West Hartford, CT 06107 is a condo home that contains 1,786 sq ft and was built in 2005. It contains 2 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. This home last sold for $495,000 in May 2022. 
 
The Zestimate for this house is $514,900. The Rent Zestimate for this home is $3,274/mo.

WOW!!! Original Model for Stonebridge!!!  This top floor end unit home faces Farmington Ave and oozes with sunlight galore.  The open floorplan makes every room the center of attention and easy to decorate.  The cherry stained cabinetry in the kitchen with stainless appls and oversized pantry are a must have. The center island countertop with elevated eating area is perfect for everyday dining. The Family Room/Dining Room combo provides an easy to stage room depending on your personal needs.  The southern daylight provides natural light that dances on the warm colored hardwood floors. The gas fireplace is a great focal point for all to enjoy.  Your friends will be envious of The Master Bedroom will an abundance of windows, custom walk in closet, timeless bathroom and overall condition. This home features an additional bedroom and separate office space with build-ins.  A separate laundry room with room for extra storage is a bonus.  Need more...the rooftop has a great gathering area with a grill!!! Whether a mid day office break or enjoying a book- this is the place to BE. During the warmer weather residents enjoy the outside setting for Happy Hour, etc. This unit has a 2 car tandem garage on level one...no need to remove the snow from your car in the morning. Upgrades galore. All appliances convey..just bring your furniture. Your easiest move yet. Conveniently located in walking distance to the Center, Elizabeth Park, restaurants, etc. A Must See.  **** No disclosure

Beautiful, warm and inviting! This freestanding condo in the coveted Reservoir community offers high ceilings, flowing rooms and lots of natural light.  The open foyer leads to the living room with hardwood floors, built-in bookshelves and a vaulted ceiling.  This flows to the eat-in gourmet cook's kitchen with Corian counters, spacious pantry, new stainless steel appliances including dual ovens, 5-burner gas stove, refrigerator and dishwasher.  The formal dining room stuns with cathedral ceiling and a wall of windows.  The main suite offers a full bath with walk-in shower and a huge walk-in closet with custom California closet.  A second bedroom suite offers a full bath with tub.  The laundry room also offers additional storage.  Part of the garage has been finished into an office with Murphy bed for the occasional visitor.  Other features include a private deck, natural gas heating, central a/c and a one car garage.  One of the best locations in the complex set in a small cul-de-sac nestled in a wooded area.  Beautiful grounds with trails located directly across the West Hartford Reservoir!  Minutes to the famed Center filled with shops and restaurants. Welcome Home!

The Heritage is luxury condo living in the heart of Blue Back Square and West Hartford Center. Shopping, dining, every-day services, top-rated healthcare and West Harford's flagship library are at your doorstep. Whole Foods is one block away. This gorgeous third floor corner unit is flooded with natural light from eastern, southern and western windows.  The open floor plan includes a gourmet kitchen with island, a living room with gas fireplace, a dining room with balcony, two bedrooms, two full baths and laundry within the unit. There is one assigned garage space under the building, additional parking in the adjacent garage and an assigned storage unit at the garage level. Concierge service/main entrance reception is provided seven days a week and beautiful community spaces greet you upon entering the building. The common area catering kitchen can be reserved for large gatherings. Are you from out of the area?  Get ready to enjoy the amazing benefits of living in Greater Hartford.  You'll find quick access to: highways, trains, Bradley International Airport, arts/culture/entertainment, hiking, recreation, mountains, lakes, coastal destinations, Boston and NYC.  It's no surprise that West Hartford is ranked nationally as a top place to live!

description: Luxury Living at Blue Back Square! One of only three of the larger models rarely available. This unit offers 3 bedrooms, 2 ½ baths, and 2,139 sqft of living in a private end unit over the heart of the hustle and bustle of the square. There is Brazilian Cherry wide plank floors throughout the open floor plan with loads of natural light and high ceilings. The Kitchen features high end appliances, stone counters, a spacious island with ample seating and a walk-in pantry / laundry room. There’s a gas fireplace and French doors leading out to a balcony from the Living Room, Large windows in the Dining Room that offer views of the shops and restaurants along Memorial Drive, and a cozy turreted seating area where you can enjoy a hot cup of coffee/tea and a good book. The primary suite offers a large bathroom with double sinks and separate tub and shower, and a large walk-in closet. The 2nd and 3rd bedrooms share a spacious full bathroom with marble floors, stone counters and subway tile. The unit comes with 2 parking spacts (69 & 70) and two storage closets (52 & 53). The Main lobby has concierge service; as well as elegant common rooms that greet you and your guests as you enter the building, with a library, media room and a community kitchen that can be reserved for private functions. Enjoy the sophisticated lifestyle this extraordinary Condo offers just steps from your door is boutique shopping, top rated restaurants, Whole Foods, movie theater, library and much more.

The location of this gorgeous condo is ideal for those looking for West Hartford center living. Go to dinner in West Hartford Center or Blue Back Square or enjoy the amenities of nearby Fernridge Park. Constructed in 2011, with over 1700 square feet of living space, this desirable end unit condo is in the most desirable spot in the Centre Commons complex.  The end unit location gifts the condo with amazing natural light, accentuating the hardwood floors throughout.  With 3 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms and storage space this condo has everything you need.  With a dedicated entrance through the attached garage opening to a foyer the first floor has its own ample sized bedroom with its own full bath.  Currently this space is being used as an office.  The main level is an open and spacious floor plan with high ceilings, a gas fireplace, and built-ins. The beautiful kitchen has an oversized island offering great utility yet is open to a large dining/living room space.  This level has a perfectly appointed half bath.  The upper level contains two bedrooms, each with their own bathroom.    This unit is prepped for the installation of an elevator if that is a priority for the future owner.  With the largest patio area in the complex, the outdoor space is beautiful and the perfect place to entertain and relax.  There’s nothing left to do but unpack!  (Inside pictures are from previous listing, currently tenant occupied.)

Sophisticated elegance in the heart of Blue Back Square!  Incredible 2 bedroom end unit plus a den/office w/window.  You will fall in love from the moment you enter this lovely unit.  Incredible open layout - kitchen w/high end appliances open to a large living room/dining room w/fireplace, lots of oversized windows for wonderful light and a French door open to a balcony.  There is a master bedroom suite w/a full bathroom that boasts double sinks, a separate tub and shower and a large walk-in closet. There is a charming guest bedroom w/a walk in closet and access to a full bath w/shower.  There is the added bonus of a perfect den/office w/a large window and built-ins for the ease of working from home.  There are 2 parking spaces (66 & 67) and a storage unit (72-B).  Enjoy all that Blue Back Square has to offer - shopping, restaurants, library, Whole Foods market and a movie theater just outside your door.  Beautiful lighting, Brazilian cherry floors throughout, custom built-ins, open layout and lots of natural light add to the perfection of this unit!  Truly a wonderful place to call home! Incredible high end furnishings can be sold separate from the sale of the unit.

MOVE IN READY!! LAST UNIT WITH 1ST FLOOR MASTER!! Harvest Village, a quaint neighborhood of 60 semi-attached and attached luxury townhomes. Perfectly styled and visually stunning ranch-style condo in a residential area near the bustling West Hartford Center and just a short walk from historic Elizabeth Park. Beautiful details throughout - reclaimed woods, gorgeous marbles and tiles, and a wonderful open floorplan with lots of space. Artfully designed Tudor style building with quality craftmanship and details. Big, bright windows illuminate the open floor plan with 9' ceilings, hardwood floors, two bedrooms PLUS an office/guest room, and luxurious updates throughout.  The living room with tall windows, French door to a balcony, and coffered ceiling features a beautiful fireplace with antique barnwood mantle, bluestone hearth and custom shiplap details.  This is open to the spacious dining area and the remodeled kitchen with an amazing 8' white marble island, Mediterranean inspired tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, deep farmers sink, and walk-in pantry.  French doors open to the master bedroom suite with custom California Closet and a spacious bath with walk-in marble shower.  In addition to another bedroom and full bath, there is another room perfect for an office or guest room! Other features include a remodeled laundry room, Gas heat, central a/c, and a tandem two-car garage space.  Privately located on the third floor of this well-maintained small complex building of only 16 units with elevator service and a rooftop patio.  Welcome Home!

description: Absolutely stunning freestanding ranch unit in the highly desirable Reservoir community, directly across the road from the West Hartford reservoir and less than a 5 minute drive to The Center brimming with shops and restaurants! Fantastic location in the complex at the end of a small cul-de-sac backing to one of the wooded trails. Step inside and be greeted by soaring ceilings, large windows and gleaming hardwood floors. The floor plan is open and flowing - perfect for entertaining, yet also has cozy areas for quiet relaxation. The living room features a marble gas fireplace and is open to the spacious eat-in kitchen with Corian counters, gas range, double oven, pantry and plenty of cabinets.  The bright formal dining room features a cathedral ceiling and plenty of room to accommodate large gatherings.  Across the foyer is the cozy study with walk-in closet.  Two ensuite bedrooms both offer walk-in closets and full baths, and the primary bath has a walk-in shower with seat.  Other features include a laundry room, private deck, an expansive unfinished basement with a NEW Lennox natural gas furnace/central a/c with transferrable warranty, security system and two car garage.  Beautifully maintained and well-planned grounds with meandering paths and trails.  Welcome Home!
